<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>活動條款得獎公告</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: auto;
      padding: 20px;
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 32px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #007bff;
    }
    .tabs {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      cursor: pointer;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .tab {
      padding: 10px 20px;
      background-color: #007bff;
      color: white;
      margin-right: 5px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      transition: background-color 0.3s;
    }
    .tab:hover {
      background-color: #0056b3;
    }
    .tab-content {
      display: none;
      margin-top: 20px;
      font-size: 18px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .tab-content.active {
      display: block;
    }
    .button {
      padding: 12px 20px;
      background-color: #007bff;
      color: white;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-size: 16px;
      text-decoration: none;
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .button:hover {
      background-color: #0056b3;
    }
  </style>
  <script>
    function showTabContent(tabId) {
      var contents = document.querySelectorAll('.tab-content');
      contents.forEach(function(content) {
        content.classList.remove('active');
      });
      document.getElementById(tabId).classList.add('active');
    }
    // 初始展示第一個tab
    document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
      showTabContent('important-info');
    });
  </script>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>得獎須知</h1>
    <div class="tabs">
      <div class="tab" onclick="showTabContent('important-info')">領獎重要事項</div>
      <div class="tab" onclick="showTabContent('winner-list')">中獎名單</div>
    </div>
    <div id="important-info" class="tab-content active">
      <h2>抽獎規則與條件 Rules and Conditions</h2>
    
      <!-- 主標題 1 -->
      <h3>指定日馬上抽  Immediate Draw on Specified Dates</h3>
      <ol>
        <li>抽獎資格 Eligibility：
          <ul>
            <li>本活動僅限通路夥伴參加。一個員工ID在每個指定日期僅能參加一次。</li>
            <li>This event is only open to channel partners. Per STAR employee ID is granted one participation to single lucky draw day.</li>
          </ul>
        </li>
        <li>抽獎機制 & 獎品類型  Lottery Mechanism & Prize Types：
          <ul>
            <li>系統將於三個指定日期(X月X日， X月X日，X月X日)，針對完成當日任務的通路夥伴進行抽獎，每日抽出價值NTD新台幣300元一卡通的獎項300名，每日中獎僅限一次，三次抽獎共計最多抽出900名得獎名額。</li>
            <li>The system will conduct a lottery on three specified dates (X month X day, X month X day, X month X day) for channel partners who complete the tasks on the day. Each day, 300 winners will be drawn to receive a EasyCard worth NTD 300. Each person can win only once per day, with a total of 900 winners across the three draws.</li>
          </ul>
        </li>
        <li>
          得獎者名單公布 Winner Announcement ：
          <ul>
            <li>得獎者名單預計將於隔天下午三點於神隊友公告。</li>
            <li>The list of winners will be announced at 3 PM on the next day on the  DTE platform.</li>
          </ul>
        </li>
        <li>獎品發放方式 Prize Distribution ：
          <ul>
            <li>菲利普莫里斯專員將到店舖發放獎勵給得獎者簽收。</li>
            <li>Philip Morris representatives will visit the stores to distribute the prizes to the winners for signing</li>
            <li>針對宜花東、外島或處於管制出入區域的店舖等，菲利普莫里斯將寄送簽收單並附上已包含郵資與回寄之資訊的信封到得獎者所在店舖，得獎者需於指定日期內回填後並寄到指定地址，待菲利普莫里斯確認報稅資訊正確之後，將以雙掛號寄發NTD $新台幣300元一卡通至店舖給予得獎者。</li>
            <li>For stores in Yilan, Hualien, Taitung, offshore islands, or restricted areas, Philip Morris will send a receipt form along with a prepaid return envelope to the winning stores. Winners must fill out and return the form by the specified date. After Philip Morris confirms the tax information is correct, the NTD 300 EasyCard will be sent to the store by registered mail.</li>
         
          </ul>
        </li>
      </ol>
    
      <!-- 主標題 2 -->
      <h3>2. 領獎時間</h3>
      <ol>
        <li>得獎者須於得獎公告後 30 日內完成領獎。</li>
        <li>
          如因個人原因無法領獎：
          <ul>
            <li>請於公告後 15 日內聯繫主辦方。</li>
            <li>主辦方將根據具體情況決定後續安排。</li>
          </ul>
        </li>
        <li>逾期未完成領獎者，將視為放棄中獎資格。</li>
      </ol>
    
      <!-- 主標題 3 -->
      <h3>3. 其他注意事項</h3>
      <ol>
        <li>
          活動主辦方保留修改活動規則及條款的權利：
          <ul>
            <li>任何修改將通過官方平台發布公告。</li>
            <li>參加者需持續關注活動更新以免錯過重要通知。</li>
          </ul>
        </li>
        <li>如發現參加者有不當行為（如作弊、偽造資料等），將立即取消中獎資格。</li>
        <li>所有獎項不得轉讓、兌換現金或折抵其他商品。</li>
      </ol>
    </div>
    
    
    
    <div id="winner-list" class="tab-content">
      <h2>得獎公告</h2>
      <p>這裡可以添加中獎名單的內容。</p>
    </div>
    <a href="/" class="button">返回主頁</a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
